summaries: This document is a Form 10-K report filed by Oracle Corporation with the United States Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) for the fiscal year ending May 31, 2025. The report includes information about Oracle's financial statements, securities registered, internal control over financial reporting, and other relevant details. The company is a large accelerated filer, and its common stock trades on the New York Stock Exchange under the symbol ORCL. As of May 31, 2025, the aggregate market value of the voting stock held by non-affiliates of Oracle Corporation was approximately $305,793,119,000. A definitive proxy statement relating to Oracle's 2025 annual meeting of stockholders is incorporated by reference into Part III of this report.
